title: Do What You Say You Will Do

description:
Episode 600 - The most common phrase I hear from people who want coaching from me is "I'm really good at starting but I'm bad at finishing. I always lose my motivation." Do you feel like you do that as well? That you don't always follow through or that you come up short of your goals? Well if that is you, this is the perfect episode for you! **If you are ready to break out of all of your comfort zones, join us in the IronMind60 Challenge and click here... www.IronMind60.com
